g unto the people, that they should believe on him which should come after him, that is, on Christ Jesus.","year":58},{"id":"rec0TDVZ1VZXzydED","ref":"Acts.19.5","text":"When they heard this, they were baptized in the name of the Lord Jesus.","year":58},{"id":"recdq319CwKkvt73M","ref":"Acts.19.6","text":"And when Paul had laid his hands upon them, the Holy Ghost came on them; and they spake with tongues, and prophesied.","year":58},{"id":"recxWp1Tx9vqqCmw8","ref":"Acts.19.7","text":"And all the men were about twelve.","year":58},{"id":"reczNTgqe13tdVFO9","ref":"Acts.19.8","text":"And he went into the synagogue, and spake boldly for the space of three months, disputing and persuading the things concerning the kingdom of God.","year":58}]}
